Source: ubuntucinnamon-meta
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Joshua Peisach <ubuntucinnamonremix7@gmail.com>
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 12), germinate (>= 2.32)
Homepage: https://github.com/Ubuntu-Cinnamon-Remix/
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/Ubuntu-Cinnamon-Remix/ubuntucinnamon-meta
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/Ubuntu-Cinnamon-Remix/ubuntucinnamon-meta.git

Package: ubuntucinnamon-minimal
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${germinate:Depends}
Recommends: ${germinate:Recommends}
Provides: ubuntucinnamon-standard, cinnamon, cinnamon-desktop, cinnamon-desktop-environment
Description: Minimal core of Ubuntu Cinnamon
 This metapackage depends on all of the packages in the Ubuntu Cinnamon minimal system,
 that is a functional command-line system with the following capabilities:
 .
  - Boot
  - Detect hardware
  - Connect to a network
  - Install packages
  - Perform basic diagnostics
 .
 It is also used to help ensure proper upgrades, so it is recommended that
 it not be removed.

Package: ubuntucinnamon-standard
Architecture: amd64 arm64 armhf
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${germinate:Depends}
Recommends: ${germinate:Recommends}
Description: CLI-only components of Ubuntu Cinnamon
 This metapackage depends on most of non-GUI packages from Ubuntu Cinnamon.
 .
 This set of packages provides a comfortable command-line Unix-like
 environment.
 .
 It is used to ensure proper upgrades, so it is recommended that it not be
 removed.

Package: ubuntucinnamon-desktop
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${germinate:Depends}
Recommends: ${germinate:Recommends}
Provides: ubuntucinnamon-standard, ubuntucinnamon-minimal, cinnamon, cinnamon-desktop, cinnamon-desktop-environment
Description: Complete desktop of Ubuntu Cinnamon
 This metapackage installs the complete Ubuntu Cinnamon desktop.
 .
 It is also used to help ensure proper upgrades, so it is recommended that
 it not be removed.
